Mr. Fujizono's most trusted man.

63
00:06:08,559 --> 00:06:09,399
I'm sorry that

64
00:06:09,399 --> 00:06:10,680
you'd dine in our humble

65
00:06:11,639 --> 00:06:12,479
countryside.

66
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:15,399
Xingkai, long time no see.

67
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,000
Oh.

68
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,360
Let me introduce you.

69
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:22,640
Mr. Yamada

70
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:25,399
was my classmate
during my study in France.

71
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,080
But now,

72
00:06:29,279 --> 00:06:30,279
If I'm not mistaken,

73
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,759
he assists Mr. Fujizono

74
00:06:33,399 --> 00:06:34,239
with stability

75
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,440
in Rong City.

76
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,159
Please,

77
00:06:47,480 --> 00:06:48,320
have a seat.

78
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,040
Given your busy schedule,

79
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,360
may I ask about purpose

80
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,200
