81
00:07:00,439 --> 00:07:03,040
It's been a while
since Mr. Fujizono took over

82
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,360
Japanese Commerce Chamber here.

83
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,360
I believe everyone present

84
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,519
can see

85
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,279
how prosperous

86
00:07:09,560 --> 00:07:11,000
Rong City has become

87
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,439
under his leadership.

88
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,160
What I mean is,

89
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,000
as leaders of Rong City's
commerce and culture,

90
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:21,360
don't you two

91
00:07:22,399 --> 00:07:23,239
think it's proper

92
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,879
to show some gratitude?

93
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,760
Of course.

94
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:36,279
However,

95
00:07:36,519 --> 00:07:37,399
